  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> 1. Custom Dice Mechanics – Archetype-Specific Rolls</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Each archetype has a unique dice system, similar to Mario Party.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Some archetypes roll higher but have drawbacks.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> Some roll consistently but have lower variability.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> The Observer and Professor also roll dice, modified by setting and exposition elements.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📖</font> Example: Archetype Dice Rolls</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Archetype</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Dice Type</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Roll Effect</div>",
